      <details>
        <summary><h2 class='section-title-collapsible'>Professional</h2></summary>
        <section id='experience'>
          <h3 class='section-subtitle'>Defense and AI Industry Experience</h3>
          {% for exp in work_experiences | selectattr('category', 'equalto', 'defense_industry') %}
          <div class='date-content-box'>
            <div class='my-dates'>{{ exp.date_display }}</div>
            <div class='content'>
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i></h4>
              <ul>
                {% for bullet in exp.bullets %}
                <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
          <h3 class='section-subtitle'>Defense and AI Research Experience</h3>
          <p>Conducted multi-year sponsored research in ML provenance, knowledge graph design, and ontology alignment (BFO/CCO). Delivered interoperable AI data schemes and explainability frameworks for defense ML pipelines. The noted dates are for physical presence with the AFRL; research was continuous, whether remote or in-person.</p>
          {% for exp in work_experiences | selectattr('category', 'equalto', 'defense_research') %}
          <div class='date-content-box'>
            <div class='my-dates'>{{ exp.date_display }}</div>
            <div class='content'>
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i></h4>
              <ul>
                {% for bullet in exp.bullets %}
                <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
          <h3 class='section-subtitle'>Applied R&D and Consulting Experience</h3>
          <p>Working remotely as owner of <a href='https://semanticscience.us'>Semantic Science</a>, delivered applied ontology, provenance, and AI knowledge-graph solutions for multiple clients across defense and enterprise domains, e.g., defense intelligence, nuclear systems, construction engineering, law, media analytics, and higher education.</p>
          <hr class='collapsed-hr'>
          {% for exp in work_experiences | selectattr('category', 'equalto', 'consulting') %}
          <div class='date-content-box'>
            <div class='my-dates'>{{ exp.date_display }}</div>
            <div class='content'>
              {% if exp.org_url is defined and exp.org_extra_in_italic is defined %}
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i><a href='{{ exp.org_url }}'>{{ exp.org }}</a>{{ exp.org_extra_in_italic }}</i></h4>
              {% elif exp.org_url is defined %}
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i><a href='{{ exp.org_url }}'>{{ exp.org }}</a></i></h4>
              {% else %}
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i></h4>
              {% endif %}
              <ul>
                {% for bullet in exp.bullets %}
                <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
          <h3 class='section-subtitle'>Graduate Positions</h3>
          {% for exp in work_experiences | selectattr('category', 'equalto', 'graduate') %}
          <div class='date-content-box'>
            <div class='my-dates'>{{ exp.date_display }}</div>
            <div class='content'>
              {% if exp.org_extra_after_italic is defined %}
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i>{{ exp.org_extra_after_italic }}</h4>
              {% else %}
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i></h4>
              {% endif %}
              <ul>
                {% for bullet in exp.bullets %}
                <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
          <h3 class='section-subtitle'>Undergrad and Prior</h3>
          {% for exp in work_experiences | selectattr('category', 'equalto', 'undergrad') %}
          <div class='date-content-box'>
            <div class='my-dates'>{{ exp.date_display }}</div>
            <div class='content'>
              <h4>{{ exp.title_line }}<i>{{ exp.org }}</i></h4>
              <ul>
                {% for bullet in exp.bullets %}
                <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </section>
      </details>
